name: photographic print, roses #1, 4x6"
description:
Photographic print of an original taken with a Pentax Spotmatic with Kodak Portra film. Printed on Fujifilm Ever Beauty paper. Available in glossy or matte finish.

4x6" in size. Can be cropped to fit in 3x5" frames.

Please note that colours may appear slightly different depending on your monitor. We ship from Japan and items may take 5-10 days.
